### GET all TODOS
GET http://localhost:4000/api/todos HTTP/1.1

### GET completed TODOS
GET http://localhost:4000/api/todos?complete='true'&limit=2

### GET all TODOS with pagination param
GET http://localhost:4000/api/todos?page=2&limit=2

### GET one TODO
GET http://localhost:4000/todos/1 HTTP/1.1

### ADD one TODO
POST http://localhost:4000/api/todos/new HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "first creation"
}

### DELETE one TODO
DELETE http://localhost:4000/todos/3 HTTP/1.1

### DELETE All todos
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/todos

### DELETE All completed TODOS
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/todos?completed=true

### UPDATE one TODO
PUT http://localhost:4000/todos/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "updated title",
  "complete": false
}